Tanzanian songbird Ray C is mourning after losing her unborn child while vacationing in France this past weekend. Ray C announced the sad news through her social media pages, where she confirmed that her unborn child was no more. The singer went on to seek advice from other mums on how to avoid a miscarriage. She wrote, "Naombeni ushauri kina mama wote nifanye mimba istoke? imeniuma! Imenibidi nishee nanyi.#mybabyisnomore #mwanangukaendazake. (I am asking for a piece of advice from mothers, how do I avoid miscarriage?)" This is the first time Ray C has come out to talk about her private life after quitting drugs.